{"tid":968693,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"半島酒店自助餐","createTime":"2019-01-04T12:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T15:45:15.000Z","uid":175988,"like":240,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":43,"replies":[{"pid":"e4b088ca2c5bbdf28381d012c96863c10ccfa984","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>露台餐廳 @ 半島酒店</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LpbY0Ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLpbY0Ch.jpg&h=00c7e212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mIZbImY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmIZbImY.jpg&h=c026b459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OXb3c74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOXb3c74.jpg&h=da45d8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyKaBXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJyKaBXo.jpg&h=be4d686c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kr2JgO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fkr2JgO2.jpg&h=ba47fcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>自助午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境典雅有氣派，侍應勤快有禮貌，服務質素高<br />\n頭盤：龍蝦沙律同煮鮑魚唔錯，龍蝦肉結實爽甜，鮑魚彈牙入味<br />\n主菜：印度咖哩幾好，香料多，濃香而唔油膩；燒西冷調味適中又夠淋，略嫌牛味不足<br />\n甜品：名物英式鬆餅保持一貫水準，鬆化有奶香，配埋新鮮果醬同clotted cream無得輸；檸檬撻同朱古力撻都係高質之作，前者帶清新酸香，後者濃厚帶苦，撻皮酥脆；雪糕同sorbet都值得一試，特別係奶茶雪糕，奶同忌廉成份較少，茶味突出帶回甘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物種類唔多，刺身無生蠔無蟹腳無原隻龍蝦，熱盤選擇更加少，雖然話貴精不貴多，但比起同一價位嘅酒店例如JW Marriott咁，食物區就明顯太細<br />\n頭盤：煙三文魚太䶢無魚油香，凍蝦同帶子太硬無鮮味<br />\nSide Dish：蛋批個餡同撻皮分離晒，唔夠蛋香，質素同coffee shop翻叮嘅差唔多<br />\n甜品：Madeleine又乾又無味，朱古力macaron過甜，入面太軟身同濃稠，完全無蛋白餅鬆脆嘅口感，唔知係咪焗得唔夠耐 (不過整體上甜品質素算高，呢兩款係例外)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: $510 per head值唔值就見仁見智，整體用餐體驗咁講就一試無妨，如果期望食物種類豐富或者味道驚為天人嘅話咁你就會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\nPS：我下個sem會去美國exchange，唔知大家有無興趣睇下當地餐廳嘅食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06a83b0e050e9509dda0cadbed397dcb4904c3a0","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":98,"dislike":3,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:29:03.000Z","msg":"參考評分：<br />\n頭盤: 7.5/10<br />\n熱盤: 7/10<br />\n甜品: 8/10<br />\n<br />\n服務: 8/10<br />\n環境: 8.5/10<br />\n<br />\nOverall: 8/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0975edf6a570846ad26461897afd9ffc456eca63","tid":968693,"uid":79481,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"半島夜晚自助餐唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係坐得舒服d同埋靜d"},{"pid":"94ec079f92d2f9eb8c2c0405c0620312a185267b","tid":968693,"uid":25776,"like":9,"dislike":62,"score":-53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"連登變埋open rice??"},{"pid":"a9757b9c07bfcb1e2e25136c8955b00e7cb22af7","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":50,"dislike":0,"score":50,"quote":{"pid":"0975edf6a570846ad26461897afd9ffc456eca63","tid":968693,"uid":79481,"like":64,"dislike":1,"score":63,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:43:20.000Z","msg":"半島夜晚自助餐唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係坐得舒服d同埋靜d"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:46:53.000Z","msg":"仲要每人過$800，咁不如食fine dining<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78dfd3f475cd224e2c6767ebdee127fcff2d9346","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":99,"dislike":1,"score":98,"quote":{"pid":"94ec079f92d2f9eb8c2c0405c0620312a185267b","tid":968693,"uid":25776,"like":9,"dislike":62,"score":-53,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:45:40.000Z","msg":"連登變埋open rice??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:48:01.000Z","msg":"Openrice啲食評質素參差<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=