{"pid":"5e450a958d7a0a2861c5cba25fef5418897f7cad","tid":968693,"uid":200738,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4b088ca2c5bbdf28381d012c96863c10ccfa984","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>露台餐廳 @ 半島酒店</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LpbY0Ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLpbY0Ch.jpg&h=00c7e212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mIZbImY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmIZbImY.jpg&h=c026b459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OXb3c74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOXb3c74.jpg&h=da45d8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyKaBXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJyKaBXo.jpg&h=be4d686c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kr2JgO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fkr2JgO2.jpg&h=ba47fcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>自助午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境典雅有氣派，侍應勤快有禮貌，服務質素高<br />\n頭盤：龍蝦沙律同煮鮑魚唔錯，龍蝦肉結實爽甜，鮑魚彈牙入味<br />\n主菜：印度咖哩幾好，香料多，濃香而唔油膩；燒西冷調味適中又夠淋，略嫌牛味不足<br />\n甜品：名物英式鬆餅保持一貫水準，鬆化有奶香，配埋新鮮果醬同clotted cream無得輸；檸檬撻同朱古力撻都係高質之作，前者帶清新酸香，後者濃厚帶苦，撻皮酥脆；雪糕同sorbet都值得一試，特別係奶茶雪糕，奶同忌廉成份較少，茶味突出帶回甘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物種類唔多，刺身無生蠔無蟹腳無原隻龍蝦，熱盤選擇更加少，雖然話貴精不貴多，但比起同一價位嘅酒店例如JW Marriott咁，食物區就明顯太細<br />\n頭盤：煙三文魚太䶢無魚油香，凍蝦同帶子太硬無鮮味<br />\nSide Dish：蛋批個餡同撻皮分離晒，唔夠蛋香，質素同coffee shop翻叮嘅差唔多<br />\n甜品：Madeleine又乾又無味，朱古力macaron過甜，入面太軟身同濃稠，完全無蛋白餅鬆脆嘅口感，唔知係咪焗得唔夠耐 (不過整體上甜品質素算高，呢兩款係例外)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: $510 per head值唔值就見仁見智，整體用餐體驗咁講就一試無妨，如果期望食物種類豐富或者味道驚為天人嘅話咁你就會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\nPS：我下個sem會去美國exchange，唔知大家有無興趣睇下當地餐廳嘅食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"如果去開 LA, 可以去試下 Bestia 同 Bavel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9dec0609f1800cab3945fc07e59c9d4c90ce6e8","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61cbd5eae448c17e84741b29e4eeee4f5365c89","tid":968693,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"去親半島一係就high tea<br />\n一係就上樓上<br />\n<br />\n真係未試過buffet <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:56:59.000Z","msg":"High tea啲scones<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過好貴，性價比極低，真係食環境氣氛同個feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e8ab03272f6b11913ca8e1e898f677264674d6","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e450a958d7a0a2861c5cba25fef5418897f7cad","tid":968693,"uid":200738,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"e4b088ca2c5bbdf28381d012c96863c10ccfa984","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T12:25:35.000Z","msg":"<strong>露台餐廳 @ 半島酒店</strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/LpbY0Ch.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FLpbY0Ch.jpg&h=00c7e212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mIZbImY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmIZbImY.jpg&h=c026b459&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OXb3c74.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOXb3c74.jpg&h=da45d8f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/JyKaBXo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJyKaBXo.jpg&h=be4d686c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/kr2JgO2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fkr2JgO2.jpg&h=ba47fcac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong>自助午餐<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n環境典雅有氣派，侍應勤快有禮貌，服務質素高<br />\n頭盤：龍蝦沙律同煮鮑魚唔錯，龍蝦肉結實爽甜，鮑魚彈牙入味<br />\n主菜：印度咖哩幾好，香料多，濃香而唔油膩；燒西冷調味適中又夠淋，略嫌牛味不足<br />\n甜品：名物英式鬆餅保持一貫水準，鬆化有奶香，配埋新鮮果醬同clotted cream無得輸；檸檬撻同朱古力撻都係高質之作，前者帶清新酸香，後者濃厚帶苦，撻皮酥脆；雪糕同sorbet都值得一試，特別係奶茶雪糕，奶同忌廉成份較少，茶味突出帶回甘<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n食物種類唔多，刺身無生蠔無蟹腳無原隻龍蝦，熱盤選擇更加少，雖然話貴精不貴多，但比起同一價位嘅酒店例如JW Marriott咁，食物區就明顯太細<br />\n頭盤：煙三文魚太䶢無魚油香，凍蝦同帶子太硬無鮮味<br />\nSide Dish：蛋批個餡同撻皮分離晒，唔夠蛋香，質素同coffee shop翻叮嘅差唔多<br />\n甜品：Madeleine又乾又無味，朱古力macaron過甜，入面太軟身同濃稠，完全無蛋白餅鬆脆嘅口感，唔知係咪焗得唔夠耐 (不過整體上甜品質素算高，呢兩款係例外)<br />\n<br />\n<strong>結論: $510 per head值唔值就見仁見智，整體用餐體驗咁講就一試無妨，如果期望食物種類豐富或者味道驚為天人嘅話咁你就會失望<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </strong><br />\n<br />\nPS：我下個sem會去美國exchange，唔知大家有無興趣睇下當地餐廳嘅食評<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:55:43.000Z","msg":"如果去開 LA, 可以去試下 Bestia 同 Bavel <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:57:34.000Z","msg":"會去LA旅行<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d33aaa18af9f4a399b2959bc53342240e2293f","tid":968693,"uid":143366,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f9dec0609f1800cab3945fc07e59c9d4c90ce6e8","tid":968693,"uid":175988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f61cbd5eae448c17e84741b29e4eeee4f5365c89","tid":968693,"uid":143366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-04T16:54:26.000Z","msg":